  "Description": {
    "English": "An oddly-glowing substance, harvested from the gills of <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Fungal Clusters</span>.<br><br>The host plant requires a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">toxic climate</span> to thrive in the wild, but can be farmed in all environments with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hydroponics Tray</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种奇怪的发光物质，可从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">真菌团</span>菌褶中收获。<br><br>宿主植物需要在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">毒性气候</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种奇怪的发光物质，可从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">真菌团</span>菌褶中收获。<br><br>宿主植物需要在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">毒性气候</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "散發出古怪光芒的物質，從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">蕈群</span>菌褶上採收而來。<br><br>這種寄主植物需要<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">劇毒氣候</span>才能在野外生長，但若借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">水耕盤</span>，便能在任何環境中栽種。"
  },
